HEADWORD: Lethargical
<hw>Le*thar"gic*al</hw> <pr>(-j⟦icr⟧*k⟦ait⟧l)</pr>, }</mhw>
<pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L. <ets>lethargicus</ets>, Gr.
